content:
Display Vlocity Actions with the Vlocity Action Toolbar.

Open cards, OmniScripts, Experience Cloud site pages, web pages, documents, and external applications on a Lightning or Experience Cloud site record page. The Vlocity Action Toolbar is no longer updated or enhanced. If you use Vlocity Actions and have Managed Package Runtime enabled, display Vlocity Actions in a FlexCard instead.

From the toolbar, click Vlocity Actions links. Record Id and permissions determine which actions show in the toolbar. Because LWC Cards and OmniScripts arenâ€™t URL addressable, use Angular Vlocity Cards and OmniScripts from the toolbar.

Add the toolbar to a Lightning record page or Experience Cloud site record page to open cards, OmniScripts, and other applications. Configure the optional properties that control the toolbar layout and available actions.
title: Displaying Vlocity Actions with OmniStudio
